caption.p: Comparative chemical profiles regarding functional group families of essential oils and hydrolate extracts from eight Paeonia suffruticosa Andr. cultivars: ( a) ‘JYH’; ( b) ‘JXQ’; ( c) ‘SHT’; ( d) ‘FDB’; ( e) ‘HH’; ( f) ‘YH’; ( g) ‘BXT’; ( h) ‘WLPS’; EO, essential oil; HE, hydrolate extract.
